private_sale_content:
The private sale allows investors to invest in narativ and benefit from a low valuation. 
But it also enables Narativ to finance its initial launch costs and improve the distribution of its supply.
public_sale_content:
The public sale is the launch of the token for any investor once the private sale is closed.
We plan to launch the token on all DEX and then rarely on the largest CEX thanks to our network.distribution of its supply.
raise_utility_content_1: $300,000 : Liquidity for the launch on uniswap
raise_utility_content_2: $100,000 : Costs related to development and Sherlock audits
